Today marks one year anniversary of my father’s passing. I am dedicating one his favourite songs - Kana Kaanum Kangal - Bamboo Perspective an old Tamil classic from the 80s composed by MS Viswanathan. 

I would like to thank Ryan Tu @ryantucreative for the wonderful videography and Himanshu Agarwal for the crisp, colorful and beautiful @hemanshoot post production. Thank you Himanshu for your patience!

Thanks to Selva @selvadrums for the audio production and TK Chandrasekaran @elvin_sc for the mix and master.

CONCERT ANNOUNCEMENT

FLUTE SIVA - Live in concert

“Experience the mesmerizing melodies of Flute Siva in a captivating live in concert. 

Join us on October 14th for an unforgettable musical journey through the evocative soundscapes of Indian cinema. 

With over 300,000 subscribers and 50 million views on his YouTube channel, Flute Siva brings his digital brilliance to the grand stage. 

Supported by a phenomenal band of acclaimed musicians, including 3 Juno award winners, prepare to be enthralled by their powerful, meditative, and orchestral renditions. 

Get ready for a symphony of enchantment that will leave you captivated. 

Don't miss this extraordinary musical extravaganza!”

@strightupjan @thibisanb @bass_416_don_473 @suren_guitar @vetrimahi @yathavan_tabla

From JS Bach to Jethro Tull to Ilaiyaraja, presented by Flute Siva @flutesiva 

'Bouree Vaa' - A Bamboo Perspective. 

Immerse yourself in a unique musical journey that spans over 300 years, as we traverse from Bach's timeless 'Bouree' to Jethro Tull's modern interpretation. Flute Siva breathes new life into this classic, offering a bamboo perspective that harmoniously transitions into Ilaiyaraja's 'Thumbi Vaa.' 

It's a fusion of musical eras and cultures that you won't want to miss. - “Bouree Vaa”

#bouree #jsbach #jethrotull #westernclassical #flute #crossculture
